						               													<description>Takeaway is a simple card based game for 2 - 6 players where the object of the game is to make money by serving as many customers and or making deliveries while the take away is open.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game play is simple - The game is played over 15 rounds. Each player has 1 turn per round. On your turn you get to perform TWO actions from the following list in any order. They can be the same action twice or two different actions.&amp;#10;1.    Pick up two Menu Item Cards&amp;#10;2.    Pick up one Delivery card&amp;#10;3.    Serve one Customer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Deliveries are worth more but the menu items are unknown to the player when they take the card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of each round move the clock one space along the time track.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Once the time token has been moved to 02.00 then all players have one more turn then the game ends. The game will also end if there are no more customers left to serve &amp;ndash; if this is the case then all players get to finish off the round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner is the player whose orders add up to the greatest value.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
